# 🚀 5️⃣ StringBuilder vs StringBuffer (IMPORTANT 🔥)

---

## 🔹 StringBuilder

* Mutable
* Fast
* Not thread-safe

---

## 🔹 StringBuffer

* Mutable
* Thread-safe
* Slower

---

## 💻 Example

```java
StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder("Hello");
sb.append(" World");

System.out.println(sb);
```

---

